hh3cDHCPServerMib.name: hh3cDHCPServerMib
hh3cDHCPServerMib.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cDHCPServerMib.description: This MIB describes objects used for managing DHCP server.

Hh3cDhcpSEnabledStatus.name: Hh3cDhcpSEnabledStatus
Hh3cDhcpSEnabledStatus.description: To descript the status of some function is Enabled or Disabled.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolTable.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolTable
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolTable.description: A table for creating DHCP server global pools.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolEntry.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolEntry
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolEntry.description: An entry containing objects for creating or deleting a global pool for the DHCP server.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolRowStatus.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolRowStatus
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolRowStatus.description: RowStatus. Three actions are used: active, createAndGo, destroy.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolConfigTable.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolConfigTable
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolConfigTable.description: A table containing the configurations of dhcp server global pools.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolConfigEntry.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolConfigEntry
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolConfigEntry.description: An entry containing the objects for configuring the network ip or host ip etc. to global pools for DHCP server.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolType.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolType
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolType.description: Type of a DHCP global pool. Any operations of this object will be bound with the operations of hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolNetwork, hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolHostIPAddr, or hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolHostHAddr. That means any operation of this object alone will be regarded as invalid operation.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolNetwork.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolNetwork
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolNetwork.description: Network ip of a DHCP global pool. To delete a configured network ip, please set hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolConfigUndoFlag to 1.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolNetworkMask.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolNetworkMask
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolNetworkMask.description: Net mask of a DHCP global pool(network). The SET operation to this object ought to be with the SET of hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolNetwork together, and any SET operation alone to this object will be regarded as an invalid operation. When a network ip of a DHCP global pool was deleted, the net mask would also be deleted automatically, and no further operation needed.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolHostIPAddr.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolHostIPAddr
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolHostIPAddr.description: Host ip of a DHCP global pool. To delete a configured network ip, please set hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolConfigUndoFlag to 2.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolHostMask.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolHostMask
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolHostMask.description: Net mask of a DHCP global pool(host) The SET operation to this object ought to be with the SET of hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolHostIPAddr together, and any SET operation alone to this object will be regarded as an invalid operation. When a host ip of a DHCP global pool was deleted, the net mask would also be deleted automatically, and no further operation needed.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolHostHAddr.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolHostHAddr
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolHostHAddr.description: Hardware address of a DHCP global pool(host). To delete a configured hardware address, please set hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolConfigUndoFlag to 3.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolConfigUndoFlag.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolConfigUndoFlag
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolConfigUndoFlag.description: Flag of undo operation for hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolConfigTable.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolParaTable.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolParaTable
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolParaTable.description: A table for configuring parameters to DHCP global pools.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolParaEntry.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolParaEntry
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolParaEntry.description: An entry containing the objects for the configurations of parameters of DHCP global pools.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolLeaseDay.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolLeaseDay
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolLeaseDay.description: Number of days of the lease.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolLeaseHour.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolLeaseHour
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolLeaseHour.description: Number of hours of the lease.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolLeaseMinute.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolLeaseMinute
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolLeaseMinute.description: Number of minutes of the lease.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolLeaseUnlimited.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolLeaseUnlimited
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolLeaseUnlimited.description: A flag denoting if the lease of a pool is unlimited.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientGatewayIPString.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientGatewayIPString
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientGatewayIPString.description: String of gateway ip addresses for DHCP clients. Since mostly 8 ip can be configured for a pool totally, a string is defined to get or configure 8 ip ip at a time.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientGatewayIPUndo.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientGatewayIPUndo
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientGatewayIPUndo.description: A gateway ip address to delete. This object is only for deleting a given ip of gateway router.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientDNSIPString.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientDNSIPString
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientDNSIPString.description: String of DNS server ip addresses for DHCP clients. Since mostly 8 ip can be configured for a pool totally, a string is defined to get or configure 8 ip at a time.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientDNSIPUndo.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientDNSIPUndo
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientDNSIPUndo.description: A DNS server ip address to delete. This object is only for deleting a given ip of DNS server.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientNetbiosType.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientNetbiosType
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientNetbiosType.description: NetBios node type for DHCP clients.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientNbnsIPString.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientNbnsIPString
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientNbnsIPString.description: String of NetBios server ip addresses for DHCP clients. Since mostly 8 ip can be configured for a pool totally, so a string is defined to get or configure 8 ip at a time.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientNbnsIPUndo.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientNbnsIPUndo
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolClientNbnsIPUndo.description: A NetBios server ip address to delete. This object is only for deleting a given ip of NetBios server.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolIPInUseReset.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolIPInUseReset
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolIPInUseReset.description: Reset the auto binding ip of the given global pool for DHCP server.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionTable.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionTable
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionTable.description: A table for configuring options to DHCP global pools.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionEntry.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionEntry
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionEntry.description: An entry containing the objects for configuring options to DHCP global pools.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionHexString.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionHexString
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionHexString.description: Hex string of an option. 1st to 16th hex strings, which are 2 bytes, 4 bytes, 6 bytes or 8 bytes, can be configured at most simultaneously. That means the format of each string must be '12', '1234', '123456' or '12345678'.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionIPString.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionIPString
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionIPString.description: Ip string of an option. 1 to 8 ip addresses can be configured at most simultaneously.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionRowStatus.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionRowStatus
hh3cDHCPSGlobalPoolOptionRowStatus.description: RowStatus. Three actions are used: active, createAndGo, destroy.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalTreeTable.name: hh3cDHCPSGlobalTreeTable
hh3cDHCPSGlobalTreeTable.description: A table containing the information of the tree of DHCP global pools.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalTreeEntry.description: An entry of objects containing the information for displaying the tree of DHCP global pools.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalTreePreSiblingNodeName.description: Pool name of the presibling node.

hh3cDHCPSGlobalTreeSiblingNodeName.description: Pool name of the sibling node.

hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolParaEntry.description: An entry of objects for configuring parameters to DHCP interface pools. The index of this entry is the ifIndex of ethernet.

hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolLeaseHour.description: Number of hours of the lease.

hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolLeaseMinute.name: hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolLeaseMinute
hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolLeaseMinute.description: Number of minutes of the lease.

hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolLeaseUnlimited.name: hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolLeaseUnlimited
hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolLeaseUnlimited.description: A flag denoting if the lease of a pool is unlimited.

hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolClientDNSIPString.description: String of DNS server ip addresses for DHCP clients. Since mostly 8 ip can be configured for a pool totally, a string is defined to get or configure 8 ip at a time.

hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolClientDNSIPUndo.description: A DNS server ip address to delete. This object is only for deleting a given ip of DNS server.

hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolClientNetbiosType.name: hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolClientNetbiosType
hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolClientNetbiosType.description: NetBios node type for DHCP clients.

hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolClientNbnsIPString.description: String of NetBios server ip addresses for DHCP clients. Since mostly 8 ip can be configured for a pool totally, so a string is defined to get or configure 8 ip at a time.

hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolClientNbnsIPUndo.name: hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolClientNbnsIPUndo
hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolClientNbnsIPUndo.description: A NetBios server ip address to delete. This object is only for deleting a given ip of NetBios server.

hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolIPInUseReset.name: hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolIPInUseReset
hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolIPInUseReset.description: Reset the auto binding ip of the given interface pool for DHCP server.

hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolOptionTable.name: hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolOptionTable
hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolOptionTable.description: A table for configuring options to DHCP interface pools.

hh3cDHCPSInterfacePoolOptionEntry.description: An entry of objects for configuring options to DHCP interface pools. The index of this entry is the ifIndex of ethernet.

hh3cDHCPSIPInUseEntry.description: An entry of objects for displaying information of ip in use for DHCP server pools.
